{"tid":937622,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"美國到底無左\"made in china\" 得唔得??","createTime":"2018-12-11T16:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T02:22:22.000Z","uid":12638,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0847419d459db7a5a3d636f2bc8e866b3584d1ad","tid":937622,"uid":12638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"岩岩係youtube睇到條片幾有趣<br />\n條片係一個長期係美國生活既大陸人 <br />\n佢決定挑戰一日唔可以用&quot;Made in china&quot;既野<br />\n個結果係佢基本上全日咩都唔用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個Walmart 90幾%既貨都係大陸造<br />\n仲有條鬼婆挑佢機話佢屋企一定無大陸野<br />\n結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完之後我睇下屋企d電器<br />\n仆街 原來真係好多都大陸製<br />\n咁以往話大陸野唔安全 唔用大陸野 既言論係咪不攻自破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我d電器又真係未爆炸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=70_vEaxzsLI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D70_vEaxzsLI&d=xC4OrMYPBrf6ZaMcVUAYhozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a334cbc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=70_vEaxzsLI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">btw 個大陸人幾有趣 比起好多香港人更有公德心</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔係五毛 打手死全家 純粹係第2個角度睇到平時睇唔到既野想分享下</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0bc873ed58ce1a1490a8d5fbc3ea5d63c4d8aaa","tid":937622,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"有咪用囉，無咗中國貨自然會有其他替代品<br />\n段片只係證明中國貨真係周街都係<br />\n<br />\n記得呢個大陸佬賣杯麵段片都幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9b9fd827f8ba8ccfc108e495a8e3a3f3b270ad","tid":937622,"uid":96874,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"唔講仲以為中國人專做慈善<br />\n免費幫人開工廠做生意"},{"pid":"95dbd8ab10be43428afea3e8f21ed16dd6420e73","tid":937622,"uid":37869,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"大把地方取代到中國<br />\n反而中國冇左西方國家的需求唔知仲生唔生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250e7c2488f41ef14ed49a4a3ff12d4aebc9c34c","tid":937622,"uid":179440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0bc873ed58ce1a1490a8d5fbc3ea5d63c4d8aaa","tid":937622,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"有咪用囉，無咗中國貨自然會有其他替代品<br />\n段片只係證明中國貨真係周街都係<br />\n<br />\n記得呢個大陸佬賣杯麵段片都幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:34:11.000Z","msg":"仲有段片用油炸鬼扮法國麵包去餐廳賣 笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeac30de5722649b38d65de44f828b70f77f187","tid":937622,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:36:44.000Z","msg":"呢個世界冇話冇咗邊個唔得"},{"pid":"f4e0b9ad213d11a822fcc92b1ffe44faac64f044","tid":937622,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:45:27.000Z","msg":"冇咗中國貨<br />\n最多咪物貨上升<br />\n唔會去到唔得囉<br />\n不過冇咗美國 連登都冇得你上"},{"pid":"a8a89f455bb95408e3253e69deaa74bf8c069d59","tid":937622,"uid":37730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:57:59.000Z","msg":"現階段未必得，純粹仲有好多生產線仲係中國入面<br />\n但事實上好多生產線都走緊佬<br />\n<br />\n發現多左made in 亞洲國家既野"},{"pid":"cdddd533e548a8050acc51b69f3d56b7862a148f","tid":937622,"uid":97240,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:03:23.000Z","msg":"幾多年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好多野都made in vietnam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋中東果啲"},{"pid":"2732dd60003710af95e665b3367eae64bec9c6bf","tid":937622,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:07:17.000Z","msg":"低技術成品<br />\n要取代有幾難<br />\n支那舊時人工平地價低先做爛市<br />\n依家2018年已經唔係咁玩法啦"},{"pid":"6f11d19d07c568865ae1603517e5c8bb9b7b2112","tid":937622,"uid":147031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:24:17.000Z","msg":"以前留學買wallmart  野真心平，叫做養到我呢個窮學生，如果買返美國本土貨，實難d 俾得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d70c8554d9d37e3858877f39effd00c86e9360e","tid":937622,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:35:08.000Z","msg":"Trump咪正正要打破呢種產業鏈囉"},{"pid":"b1ab1405b6ea921d2e94abb562deb9d6b1b11b92","tid":937622,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f11d19d07c568865ae1603517e5c8bb9b7b2112","tid":937622,"uid":147031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:24:17.000Z","msg":"以前留學買wallmart  野真心平，叫做養到我呢個窮學生，如果買返美國本土貨，實難d 俾得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:42:34.000Z","msg":"打仗個陣明明咩都係Made In USA<br />\n係打完之後個個都縱容支那所以搞到要依賴佢<br />\n尤其是個Nixon 賣國賊"},{"pid":"098e17382afe033ecba96aadcf883791ecc2b2fc","tid":937622,"uid":4709,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:46:16.000Z","msg":"難，但到真係唔入口時自然有替代品<br />\n<br />\nThailand, vietnam, cambodia <br />\n南美都平"},{"pid":"9c0cb36c3db47feee8d054bfc0d88ae05b51b3f3","tid":937622,"uid":179137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de419c740dc394acca52340c391c8dc7a70782eb","tid":937622,"uid":131963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"無話唔得，可以轉移工廠去東南亞，東歐同墨西哥.<br />\n但中國有優勢係由原材料到成品，都可以一站式搞定，又無工會係到.  再加上班人肯做肯開OT.<br />\n<br />\n如果轉左其他國家， 運費首先一定會上升， 管理資源也會同時增加.  單講墨西哥同東歐既工廠， 人工係低，但歐洲人既文化 同 墨西哥既治安.  都會令成本上升.<br />\n<br />\n美國大企業最後要接受成本上升但不能加價既最終結果.  而ebit一低， 董事長班人會吊哂鬼...<br />\n<br />\n不過呢樣野會變成top management既常規玩法.<br />\n10幾廿年前， 會玩由歐美生產線搬黎東南亞，因為cost reduction.<br />\n<br />\n現在就要由東南亞， 再部份搬番去歐美，因為稅務優惠/政治原因.<br />\n<br />\n再十年後，又會因為要cost reduction， 而又搬番去東南亞....top management 就係不停做呢野樣， 玩幾轉就退得休了."}]}